QUESTION: Billy and Suzy inherited an unusual type of hybrid car that has two special car batteries called Bartlett batteries. The car won't start unless it has at least one Bartlett battery. Since all the car needed was at least one Bartlett battery, they were able to start the car. Did Billy cause the car to be able to start?
ANSWER: yes
